# multiple remove_headers in routers, and trailing colons
exim -odi userx
Remove-Me: this header is to be removed
Another: This is another header
****
exim -odi userx
Remove-Me: this header is to be removed
Another: This is another header
Remove-Me-Also: me too!
Remove-Me-Too: me too!
Remove-Me-Too2: me too!
****
